the user’s Internet Protocol address (IP address), geolocation, a unique user ID, version of software installed, system type, the content and pages accessed on the website, dates and times of visits to the website, time zone, the user’s accounts on social networks (including profile picture and information on education, job, marital status); tokens for access to the user’s accounts on social networks, accounts on social networks of friends of the user (including nicknames, profile pictures), history of payments made via the website, fingerprint of the user’s device and IP (identification of position) at time of a payment;
